{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"195","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"公司治理評鑑指標　有吹哨者檢舉制度加分","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;'>台灣證券交易所公告明年公司治理評鑑指標，設定加重給分題，若訂有「吹哨者檢舉制度」的公司將獲得加分。</span><br style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;' />\n<br style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;' />\n<span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;'>證交所表示，明年公司治理評鑑指標共有4大構面、85項指標，適用期間自明年1月1日至12月31日，並預計在2019年4月底前公布明年評鑑結果。</span><br style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;' />\n<br style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;' />\n<span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;'>證交所指出，明年評鑑參酌國際重要公司治理發展趨勢、國內新修正法規及回應各界建議，包括參考G20/OECD公司治理原則，將「維護股東權益」及「平等對待股東」構面予以合併，調整為4大構面，並配合指標數調整各構面權重。</span><br style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;' />\n<br style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;' />\n<span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;'>另外，為持續提升鑑別度，本次調整指標題型與計分方式，例如取消C題型，新增加重給分「AA題型」、依執行程度分級給分的「A＋題型」，及構面外另設「額外加分題」及「額外減分題」等。</span><br style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;' />\n<br style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;' />\n<span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;'>證交所解釋，本次配合法規修正刪除多項基本法遵題，並將部分意旨相近的指標進行整併，透過調整指標題型的方式，持續提升評鑑的鑑別度。例如將「公司是否在會計年度結束後2個月內公布年度財務報告」、「提供英文年度財務報告」及「訂定吹哨者檢舉制度」等6項指標列為加重給分題。</span><br style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;' />\n<br style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;' />\n<span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;'>另將9項指標調整為分級給分題，例如「公司揭露過去2年二氧化碳或其他溫室氣體年排放量」構面內可得分，若「揭露內容係取得外部驗證」總分可另加1分，增強採行相關措施的鼓勵效果。</span><br style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;' />\n<br style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;' />\n<span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;'>此外，為持續推動董事會職能發揮，本次也新增包括「每次董事會至少1席獨立董事親自出席」、「設置公司治理專職人員負責公司治理相關事務」，及「揭露董事績效評估與薪資報酬連結」等指標。</span><br style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;' />\n<br style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;' />\n<span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma; font-size: 18px;'>為強化企業社會責任落實，新增「設置適當企業社會責任治理架構」、「制訂保障人權政策」、「制訂政策將經營績效或成果反映於員工薪酬」等多項指標。（中央社）</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><font color='#000000' face='微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MicrosoftJhengHei, Verdana, 微軟正黑體, sans-serif, 微軟儷黑體, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, MyriadPro, Microsoft, bauerbodonistd-roman, CenturyGothic, Asap, Futura, Lucida Grande, Geneva, Helvetica, sourcehansans-tc-normal, sans-serif, Tahoma'><span style='font-size: 18px;'>資料來源:</span></font>https://news.tvbs.com.tw/politics/842733</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2017-12-29","clk_count":"290"}},"__N_SSG":true}